{
  "stem": "12003.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to fantasize, when we grow up, what we will do and where we will go.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We used to try to observe the high holidays.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were-- I remember singing with my father and my sisters, sort of like an entertainment for people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We used to try to entertain ourselves in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was an orphanage in the ghetto, I remember, where my mother used to take food, whatever we could spare, and share.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then I remember, also-- I don't how that-- pogrom.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know how you say it in English.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It just escaped me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They used to come into ghetto with big trucks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they used to create a tremendous chaos.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember my father used to come and tell us children, lock the door.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have to go outside, but you lock the door.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Don't let anybody in, and try to hide.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then my mother puts us under the beds, behind credenzas.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we used to sit there for hours.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we used to hear screaming and shooting outside.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And what was happening, they were with trucks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I guess whomever they could catch-- it was like like an animal hunt-- they used to load up in those trucks and take them outside the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the following day, we could hear that-- rather, we never heard from those people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But it was from the beginning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then we heard that they were sent out to some kind of forced labor camps.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And that used to happen repeatedly and repeatedly.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And whoever that did not get a identification card that they were somehow employed by the factories that the SS used to own, they were just taken out from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
